window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's time for Alex to officially move into his new home in Colorado, as new associates join him in developing FAE in reality.</p> <p>Meanwhile, in Eternal Dominion, he continues to move forward with his quest to gain the approval of Niumâ€™s nobility in the final year before he is to be wed to Princess Enye. Meanwhile, he is also getting to know the two other princesses from foreign nations while tracking down a few potential boosts to his guild in the form of a pair of phoenixes.</p> <p>As always, this series contains a no smut harem that seems to be getting out of control, but is really just settling into what it will truly be.</p> <p>So, join Alex/Xeal for another installment of Eternal Dominion as he takes another step in his journey to the top, with his friends and family along for the ride.</p>"; 
